==English==
===Noun===
'''djinn'''

# a [[supernatural]] being with extraordinary powers that usually takes a human form and serves its summoner: [[genie]], [[jinni]], d'jin, d'jinn

N.B.: the Arabic word ''djinn'' may be the origin of the name of the strong alcoholic spirit known as "[[Gin]]" (from the beverage's tendency to cause its imbiber to be profoundly affected by the powerful spirit).